Imenyekanisha ryo kwihangira imirimo

17
00:01:10,028 --> 00:01:12,313
Iriryo, nko,
kubona abakiriya ba mbere,

18
00:01:12,313 --> 00:01:14,082
kubona sosiyete yihagije,

19
00:01:14,082 --> 00:01:15,539
kuzamura sosiyete yawe
mu ntera.

20
00:01:15,539 --> 00:01:17,297
Hanyuma icyumweru cya 4,
Twavuze ku imari.

21
00:01:17,297 --> 00:01:19,978
Sibyo; bityo kuzamura 
no kugenzura amafaranga,

22
00:01:19,978 --> 00:01:22,992
twavuze cyane kubyerekeye
ubwoko butandukanye bw' abashoramari

23
00:01:22,992 --> 00:01:24,690
Twavuze kw' ingano
y' amafaranga wazakenera,

24
00:01:24,690 --> 00:01:26,435
ukoze igereranywa ry' imari wazakenera,

25
00:01:26,435 --> 00:01:29,432
ushaka amafaranga,
gukomeza kugenzura amafaranga yawe.

26
00:01:29,432 --> 00:01:32,514
Ndetse, no gushyiraho 
uburyo bwo gushaka inkunga mubantu benshi.

27
00:01:32,514 --> 00:01:36,462
Ariko—byanabyo, kandi uraziko,
byose are byiza,

28
00:01:36,462 --> 00:01:38,522
- ariko ugomba gufata agaciro,
- Sibyo.

29
00:01:38,522 --> 00:01:41,405
kuko udafashe agaciro
kibyo uri guhanga,

30
00:01:41,405 --> 00:01:43,142
mubyukuri, undi muntu
azagafata.

31
00:01:43,142 --> 00:01:45,951
Bityo,  mu yandi magambo,
uri gukorera undi muntu.

32
00:01:45,951 --> 00:01:48,438
Bityo, muri aka gace,
tugiye kuvuga kugufata agaciro,

33
00:01:48,438 --> 00:01:50,741
bishatse kuvuga ko, mubyukuri,
Hari ingingo,

34
00:01:50,741 --> 00:01:52,653
nubundi buryo bwa koreshwa

35
00:01:52,653 --> 00:01:54,651
bityo kagaciro kibyo ukora
kaza kuri wowe,

36
00:01:54,651 --> 00:01:55,673
atari undi muntu.

37
00:01:55,673 --> 00:01:59,276
Kandi ninabyo warikwiye
kuko kugeza ubu umaze gukora cyane

38
00:01:59,276 --> 00:02:00,596
kuri iyi nyigisho.

39
00:02:00,596 --> 00:02:04,106
kubwiyo mpamvu uburyo bumwe wakoresha kugirango ubone agaciro,

40
00:02:04,106 --> 00:02:06,546
Cyangwa se uburyo bw' ibanze
byo kubona unyungu mubyukora

41
00:02:06,546 --> 00:02:09,231
n' ukurinda igitekerezo cyawe.

42
00:02:09,231 --> 00:02:11,487
Bityo, muri 5.1, ibyo tugiye gukora

43
00:02:11,487 --> 00:02:14,553
n' ugutekereza kumitungo kamera,

44
00:02:14,553 --> 00:02:17,191
uburyo ikora,
n' impamvu tuyifite,

45
00:02:17,191 --> 00:02:19,749
n' impamvu ibihugu bitandukanye
bifite amategeko atandukanye ayerekeyeho

46
00:02:19,749 --> 00:02:21,417
ndetse nicyo bishatse kuvuga

47
00:02:21,417 --> 00:02:23,083
Bityo ni gute warinda igitekerezo cyawe

48
00:02:23,083 --> 00:02:24,965
ukoresheje uburyo butandukanye
bw' umutungo kamere?

49
00:02:24,965 --> 00:02:26,854
Mubyukuri. kandi ushobora
kuba ufite ibitekerezo bitandukanye,

50
00:02:26,854 --> 00:02:29,858
Bityo ntago ibitekerezo byose
bikwiye gushinganwa muri reta.

51
00:02:29,858 --> 00:02:32,147
Ariko hari ubundi buryo,
turaza kubivugaho

52
00:02:32,147 --> 00:02:33,913
Sibyo, turaza kubicamo byose.

53
00:02:33,913 --> 00:02:36,774
Bityo uburenganzira bw' umuhanzi ni uburyo bumwe
bwo kurinda igitekerezo cyawe,

54
00:02:36,774 --> 00:02:39,330
no kugeregeza kureba neza ko
wabonye agaciro kose 

55
00:02:39,330 --> 00:02:41,066
muburyo bwawe bw' iterambere

56
00:02:41,066 --> 00:02:43,414
Hari ubundi buryo,
mugice cya 5.2,

57
00:02:43,414 --> 00:02:45,657
tuvuga kuzindi nzira.

58
00:02:45,657 --> 00:02:48,391
Bishobora kuba byaterwa nuko
waba ufite uburyo bwo gushaka umusaruro bugoye

59
00:02:48,391 --> 00:02:50,207
abandi bantu batashobora kwitegereza,

60
00:02:50,207 --> 00:02:54,235
cyangwa igicuruzwa kigoranye
kititeguye gukoreshwa byorushye.

61
00:02:54,235 --> 00:02:56,643
nabandi bakozi,
nabo mupinganwa.

62
00:02:56,643 --> 00:02:58,199
Kandi hari
nutundi tuntu

63
00:02:58,199 --> 00:02:59,691
washaka kwitaho.

64
00:02:59,691 --> 00:03:02,990
Sibyo, nshatse kuvuga ko, hari ikibazo
cyo kuyobora imitungo y' ingenzi.

65
00:03:02,990 --> 00:03:04,038
Urazi, urugero,

66
00:03:04,038 --> 00:03:07,135
niba ukeneye ikintu
cyo gukoresha kugira ngo ucuruze igihangano cyawe,

67
00:03:07,135 --> 00:03:09,748
kandi ukaba ugifite
mubushobozi bwawe.

68
00:03:09,748 --> 00:03:11,631
Mu yandi magambo,
ufite amahitamo hagati yabantu

69
00:03:11,631 --> 00:03:14,293
Ninde wundi wabigukorera, noneho
kandi mubyukuri urikuvugira muri rusange,

70
00:03:14,293 --> 00:03:17,095
ugiye gukorera amafaranga menshi
aturutse mugihangano cyawe.

71
00:03:17,095 --> 00:03:19,289
Cyangwa bigaterwa nuko
hari umubare muto gusa

72
00:03:19,289 --> 00:03:22,103
wa sosiyete ziyobora
ibyo ukeneye kugira ngo ucuruze.

73
00:03:22,103 --> 00:03:25,322
Ahari uri umwe mubafite
imwe muri iyo mitungo.

74
00:03:25,322 --> 00:03:28,382
Niba utariwe, ushobora 
kuzayishyurira, iyo niyo ntumbero.

75
00:03:28,382 --> 00:03:31,170
Bityo hari uburyo bw' isesenguro
bikwiye kumvikana,

76
00:03:31,170 --> 00:03:34,634
Ni gute wakunguka cyane
wifatanyije abandi

77
00:03:34,634 --> 00:03:37,099
bantu batandukanye ndetse ninganda ziri hano hanze.

78
00:03:37,099 --> 00:03:39,978
Kandi nubwo bitakunda
kuri wowe muri ubwo buryo,

79
00:03:39,978 --> 00:03:43,128
wakomeza gukorera amafaranga
muguhita ukomerezaho byihuse.

80
00:03:43,128 --> 00:03:45,444
Bityo tugiye kugarira ubwo
buryo bunyuranye byose

81
00:03:45,444 --> 00:03:46,989
muri kariya gace.

82
00:03:46,989 --> 00:03:49,125
Muburyo bwo gufata agaciro,
Ntukwiye gutekereza gusa

83
00:03:49,125 --> 00:03:52,518
kubyo ucuruza
ndetse nibyo ufite, nibindi nibindi.

84
00:03:52,518 --> 00:03:55,345
Ukwiye no gutekereza kubyerekeye
nuko reta ibibona muri rusange.

85
00:03:55,345 --> 00:03:59,872
Bityo muri 5.3, tuzavuga byeguye
kubyerekeranye nuburyo reta ibibona.

86
00:03:59,872 --> 00:04:01,936
- nko—
- kugenzura igicuruzwa.

87
00:04:01,936 --> 00:04:07,512
Urugero, ukora iki
iyo icyo ucuruza kigize ingaruka kubantu--

88
00:04:07,512 --> 00:04:08,517
Mubyukuri.

89
00:04:08,517 --> 00:04:10,730
nubwo waba igicoresha neza
cyangwa nabi?

90
00:04:10,730 --> 00:04:13,222
Cyangwa ubwoko rw' imirwi iteza sosiyete imbere
waba ushaka kugira

91
00:04:13,222 --> 00:04:17,411
kugira ngo ugabanye umutwaro ukujyaho,
kuburyo udakurikiranywa

92
00:04:17,411 --> 00:04:19,887
hagize ikiba
mugihe uri gukora ubucuruzi.

93
00:04:19,887 --> 00:04:23,802
Bityo muri rusange, tuzavuga
kubyerekeranye no kuganira n' umwavoka,

94
00:04:23,802 --> 00:04:25,938
ndetse n' ubwoko bw' ibibazo
uzakenera kuvugaho

95
00:04:25,938 --> 00:04:27,172
n' umwavoka wawe.

96
00:04:27,172 --> 00:04:28,894
Tuzabyumva ko wowe,
nka rwiyemezamirimo,

97
00:04:28,894 --> 00:04:31,184
ushaka guhanga ibintu,
ugahanga ikintu kiza and gishya,

98
00:04:31,184 --> 00:04:33,624
- Bityo ibishobora kutakunyura—
- Hahaha!

99
00:04:33,624 --> 00:04:35,096
ariko wumve neza akagace

100
00:04:35,096 --> 00:04:38,067
kuko twabonye sosiyete
zihomba muri uko gutangira.

101
00:04:38,067 --> 00:04:40,353
Bakoze ibindi bintu byose neza,
ariko mugutangira,

102
00:04:40,353 --> 00:04:42,236
muburyo bwemewe n; amategeko,
barahomba.

103
00:04:42,236 --> 00:04:44,702
Bityo muri ubwo buryo,
burimo guhomba

104
00:04:44,702 --> 00:04:47,994
kuko batashobora ga
kwirinda ubwabo muburyo bwemewe n' amategeko.

105
00:04:47,994 --> 00:04:52,979
Bityo agace kanyuma muri 5
ni 5.4: Umwikarago no gukura.

106
00:04:53,479 --> 00:04:58,087
Ubu kugira ngo ubone agaciro kibyo ukora,
ushabora gukenera guhindura

107
00:04:58,087 --> 00:05:00,922
ibyo uri gukora,
cyangwa ugakenera gukura cyane.

108
00:05:00,922 --> 00:05:03,130
Bityo tugiye kuvugana birambuye
ibyerekeye ibi bintu byombi.

109
00:05:03,130 --> 00:05:04,776
Icyambere tuzavuga kubyerekeye umwikarago.

110
00:05:04,776 --> 00:05:08,134
Mu yandi magambo, guhindura bumwe muburyo
ukoresha mu bucuruzi bwawe

111
00:05:08,134 --> 00:05:10,204
kugira ngo ubyaze umusaruro
amahirwe mashya,

112
00:05:10,204 --> 00:05:11,683
cyangwa uhindure ibyo wakoraga,

113
00:05:11,683 --> 00:05:14,160
kuko ibyo uri gukora kugeza ubu
bitagenze neza.

114
00:05:14,160 --> 00:05:16,665
Kandi bikaba binahura nibyo
twaganiriye mu cyumweru cya kabiri

115
00:05:16,665 --> 00:05:17,995
mu gihe twavugaga
kubyerekeye amahirwe

116
00:05:17,995 --> 00:05:19,769
n' amahirwe menshi
washobora kubona,

117
00:05:19,769 --> 00:05:21,561
kuko bishatse kuvuga ko
ufite inzira ya 2

118
00:05:21,561 --> 00:05:24,958
nandi mahirwe yiteguye,
kandi ahamye,

119
00:05:24,958 --> 00:05:27,191
ahantu hateguye
wageragereza igihangano cyawe.

120
00:05:27,372 --> 00:05:30,525
Neza! noneho,
turaza no kuvuga kubyerekenye kwaguka.

121
00:05:30,525 --> 00:05:34,118
Turaza kuvuga ibyerekeye uburyo bwo kwaguka
kugira ngo bukuzamure,

122
00:05:34,118 --> 00:05:36,689
kandi turaza kuvuga
kubyerekeye ibibazo bishimishije

123
00:05:36,689 --> 00:05:38,945
wazagira
mu gihe wa kwaguka,

124
00:05:38,945 --> 00:05:41,112
kuko waba ukeneye
gukora impinduka

125
00:05:41,112 --> 00:05:43,612
zishyira uburyo bwa genzura
sosiyete.

126
00:05:43,612 --> 00:05:46,331
- Washobora gukenera kuyobora --
- Kuyobora cyane.

127
00:05:46,331 --> 00:05:48,076
Ukeneye kureka
ubushobozi buke kubyo uyobora.

128
00:05:48,076 --> 00:05:50,500
Kandi ibyo ni bintu byiza
bikubaho

129
00:05:50,500 --> 00:05:51,966
mu gihe sosiyete yawe
iri kwaguka cyane,

130
00:05:51,966 --> 00:05:55,331
Bityo tuzaganira
ku bibazo byo kwaguka.

131
00:05:55,871 --> 00:06:00,384
Bityo mu cyumweru cya 5 mubyukuri
cyerekeye mukubona agaciro gashoboka

132
00:06:00,384 --> 00:06:01,908
gaturuka mu bihangano byawe

133
00:06:01,908 --> 00:06:04,507
Kubw' iyo mpamvu iyo ubitekereje ho,
mubyukuri ni nko kugira ikamba ry'amabuye y' agaciro

134
00:06:04,507 --> 00:06:07,071
- mubyawe kugira ngo urifate kandi uvuge--
- Ta dah!

135
00:06:07,071 --> 00:06:09,834
"We! sindi 
guhimba ikintu gishya gusa,

136
00:06:09,834 --> 00:06:11,569
"Natangiye ku cyungukamo.

137
00:06:11,569 --> 00:06:13,830
Ndetse na nahanga imwungu kubwanjye!"

138
00:06:13,830 --> 00:06:17,160
Sibyo; bityo, gumana natwe
ku cyumweru cya 5.
